data.description: Step into your own piece of paradise with this 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath second floor condo that is ready for you to move in and enjoy. From new appliances to a fresh kitchen sink, new carpet, and freshly painted walls, every detail has been thoughtfully upgraded to provide you with a true beachfront living experience.Both bedrooms boast generous closet space, with the master bedroom featuring 2 closets for added convenience. This unit has an abundance of features to fall in love with, perfectly complemented by the resort's offerings such as 2 pools (1 heated) tennis courts, his/her sauna's, hot tubs, showers and coed fitness room.As you step onto the tiled balcony, panoramic views of the surrounding beauty await you whether you're gazing from the master bedroom or the inviting living room. The fully stocked kitchen offers ample space, and a spacious coat closet in the entryway, as well as an additional storage closet, ensure that your organizational needs are well met, whether it's linens or extra beach towels.This exclusive condo stands apart with its unique covered gazebo by the water, numerous BBQ grills throughout the complex and rear gate access, complete with a remote for easy entry, ensures your privacy and security.Additional storage off the balcony is tailored to accommodate your beach essentials, from chairs to floats, ensuring that everything you need for beachside leisure is always at hand. This unit has never been on the rental program since it was built but similar units in this building gross between 40-60k+. VA Loan possibly assumable.
